                  "code": "\twells \u003d []\n\t\n#\twell \u003d []\n#\twell.append(\u0027Site\u0027)\n#\twell.append(\u0027Flow\u0027)\n#\twell.append(\u0027DP\u0027)\n#\twell.append(\u0027SP\u0027)\n#\twell.append(\u0027Temp\u0027)\n#\twell.append(\u0027Status\u0027)\n#\twells.append(well)\n\t\n\tsites \u003d [\u0027Site A\u0027,\u0027Site B\u0027,\u0027Site C\u0027,\u0027Site D\u0027]\n\tfor site in sites:\n\t\twell \u003d {}\n\t\twell[\u0027Site\u0027] \u003d site\n\t\twell[\u0027Flow\u0027] \u003d system.tag.readBlocking([\u0027[default]Exchange/Oil And Gas Demo/Wells/%s/Flow\u0027 %site])\n\t\twell[\u0027DP\u0027] \u003d system.tag.readBlocking([\u0027[default]Exchange/Oil And Gas Demo/Wells/%s/DP\u0027 %site])\n\t\twell[\u0027SP\u0027] \u003d system.tag.readBlocking([\u0027[default]Exchange/Oil And Gas Demo/Wells/%s/SP\u0027 %site])\n\t\twell[\u0027Temp\u0027] \u003d system.tag.readBlocking([\u0027[default]Exchange/Oil And Gas Demo/Wells/%s/Temp\u0027 %site])\n\t\twell[\u0027Status\u0027] \u003d \u0027OK\u0027\n\t\twells.append(well)\n\t\n\treturn wells",
